title: Distribution of FUCD coins to Initial Investors
body:
This first proposal is to provide recognition that 10 individuals have given a total of 1.625 ETH to the Gnosis Safe fucd.eth (0x23f223C8a3eafb87628cB3B7f6985B7B5e164AaD) and to distribute those members, as recorded in this *[google document](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JY_3rdLD8WVJWdn2oJrdXK625PNW5J6qlBa3T322h1k/edit?usp=sharing)*, FUCD coins using the following ratio:

**.125 ETH : 125 FUCD**
